{"about_the_game":"In this cozy and colorful game, the player needs to surpass high scores set in various rigged Arcade Games inhabited by a residing Ghost.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/sadgif.gif?t=1737844232\" /><br><br>Explore a hand-painted 3D environment blending the childish nature of the Ghost's character with the retro aesthetic of a 1980s Arcade Hall.<br><br>Play the Story or Arcade Mode!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story:</h2><br>As you progress through the story of the game, the Ghost starts revealing their backstory.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/angygif.gif?t=1737844232\" /><br><br>Eventually, you as the player help them move on from their unfinished business.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/remorsegif.gif?t=1737844232\" /><br><br>Earn tickets from the Arcade Games to spend them in the Points Shop!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761940/extras/shopgif.gif?t=1737844232\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Arcade:</h2><br>Get instant access to all Arcade Games to compete with other players!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Us:</h2><br>We are Game Development Students from the University of Applied Sciences Darmstadt, Germany.<br><br>Currently, we are 8 people on the internal team, and 2 sound-students, working on four new Arcade Games simultaneously while also patching up the current game and working on other features and content updates.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Having a chat!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2761940/6fb5b26fe4ca71545ecfd31890a598b76167a552.jpg"},{"name":"No more llamas!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2761940/3aba60953c0d932e3de2e314d5ca50